<h2 id="ref">ref</h2>
<p>创建单个对象的响应对象，取值/赋值时需要使用.value</p>
<pre><code>const count = ref(0)
console.log(count.value) // 0
count.value++
console.log(count.value) // 1

</code></pre></li>
